channel.title: SLAM FUNK - Hot Dog [Collab?] [WIP]
channel.description:
Hey everybody!
I was wondering if any of you would be interested in collaborating with me on a song. I set up a few instruments and loops for you to use. I will let you do anything you want to do with this song!! Turn up the tempo, turn it down, et cetra. You can do anything, as long as you use some of the stuff I made. I will edit it a little or add things after I get a finished product. Surprise me and have fun!
P.S. - If I get multiple Hot Dogs, I will make an EP for them. I will make my own version of Hot Dog as well. Also if you have any questions, Feel free to ask me. üòÄ
(I will put Hot Dog in my "Oh" album out soon, if I get multiple, I will put my favorite one in.)
Here is the song: https://app.auxy.co/projects/QkraT6J8nbs9eHn2kVo82g==
